  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Implant placement may trigger bone trauma, which might result in 3-dimensional bone changes.
      While the process of peri-implant disease is not well understood, implant position within the
      bony structure might play a role. However, there is no data available on this regard.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
